  "texts": [
    "I am not claiming that such a model is available right now -but I am claiming that this model is already now conceivable and likely to be available in the foreseeable future.",
    "Notably, even with this extremely advanced model, one that does all the heavy linguistic lifting needed, it is clear that the model intends nothing with its going-ons.",
    "The model is not hungry, it does not desire to eat Chinese food, or to shield the workers in the restaurant from racial slurs, and it also doesn't intend to put something to eat in front of the racist.",
    "Rather, the model just functions (or malfunctions).",
    "It would be comical to assume that it deliberately mistranslates to order something that the racist likely does not want to eat."
  ],
